%% Order lifecycle state machine (PrintHub).
%% Render: https://mermaid.live  → export PNG.  Or paste into draw.io (Insert ▸ Advanced ▸ Mermaid).
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Draft
    Draft --> Quoted: compare quotes
    Quoted --> AwaitingAcceptance: place order (wallet debit + snapshot)
    Quoted --> Expired: 24h elapsed
    AwaitingAcceptance --> Accepted: shop accepts
    AwaitingAcceptance --> Declined: shop declines / full refund
    AwaitingAcceptance --> Cancelled: customer cancels / full refund
    Accepted --> InProduction: start production (publish job to RabbitMQ)
    Accepted --> Cancelled: cancel (cancellation fee)
    InProduction --> ReadyForPickup: agent completed (pickup)
    InProduction --> OutForDelivery: agent completed (delivery)
    InProduction --> ProductionFailed: agent failure event
    ProductionFailed --> InProduction: retry (no charge)
    ProductionFailed --> Declined: give up / full refund
    ReadyForPickup --> Completed: hand over (commission recorded)
    OutForDelivery --> Completed: delivered
    Completed --> [*]
    Declined --> [*]
    Cancelled --> [*]
    Expired --> [*]
